OFA Fiscal Note
State Impact: None
Municipal Impact:
Municipalities Effect FY 27 $ FY 28 $
Hartford Grand List See Below See Below
Impact
Explanation
The bill allows Hartford to delay an October 1, 2026 revaluation by
one year. This shifts any costs associated with revaluation and any
subsequent grand list changes into the future, provided the municipal
legislative body approves the delay.
The Out Years
The annualized ongoing fiscal impact identified above would
continue into the future subject to inflation.
